Actual results:

Hard without knowing what the dimensions are -- no popup is shown.

Expected results:

Easy as the centered popup shows the current dimensions.

Additional info:

The xfce4-terminal-0.6.3-9.fc24.x86_64 works fine and downgrading to it brings the dimension popup back.</thetext>
